<section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">How It Works</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base text-slate-700">
    We keep the process simple so non-technical business owners can move quickly and confidently.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 space-y-4">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">1. Chat</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">You explain your business goals in plain language. We ask practical questions and listen first.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">2. Plan</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">You receive a clear plan with scope, timing, and cost options. No hidden complexity.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">3. Build</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">We use AI-assisted workflows to speed up delivery while experienced engineers check quality and security.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">4. Launch</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">We test, launch, and help your team start using the new website or app with confidence.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">5. Support</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Optional ongoing support keeps everything current as your business needs evolve.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <%= link_to "Get a Free Plan", "#{contact_path}#audit-form", class: "inline-flex rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-emerald-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-emerald-600" %>
  </div>
</section>
